OL,6,FThe plans to use Black Rock come as
OL,7,Fthe current storage site at Longue
OL,8,FHogue is already at capacity -
OL,9,Fsomething the island's construction
OL,10,Findustry has warned could have huge
OL,11,Fimplications on the economy if an
OL,12,Falternative wasn't found.
OL,14,FHowever, the Committee for Environment
OL,15,Fand Infrastructure (E&I) think the new
OL,16,Fsite at Black Rock could soon be a
OL,17,Fprime site for housing too.
