OL,4,Cunits at Black Rock
OL,6,FCommittee president, Deputy Lindsay de
OL,7,FSausmarez, said: "The plans for Black
OL,8,FRock are the GDA's plans, not the
OL,9,FStates.
OL,11,F"Our involvement is that we are
OL,12,Fresponsible for the waste strategy and
OL,13,Fwe realised, along with the GDA, that
OL,14,FBlack Rock would be the best strategic
OL,15,Fuse for our waste and it would bring
OL,16,Fwith it wider developments as well.
OL,18,F"The GDA is prioritising housing at
OL,19,Fthe Bridge because it thinks it has
OL,20,Fthe most potential and can be realised
OL,21,Fquicker."
