OL,6,FDeputy de Sausmarez made clear that a
OL,7,Ffull environmental impact assessment
OL,8,Fwill take place before any specific
OL,9,Fplans are in place.
OL,11,FAlthough there are concerns that any
OL,12,Fform of new housing development could
OL,13,Faffect the biodiversity - particularly
OL,14,Fon the island's coastlines.
OL,16,FJessi Jennings, CEO of the Nature
OL,17,FCommission, said: "In Guernsey, we are
OL,18,Freally lucky to have seagrass beds
OL,19,Faround both the east coast and the
OL,20,Fwest coast.
