OL,6,F"It's really important that decisions
OL,7,Fneed to be evidenced-based so we know
OL,8,Fwhat the environmental impacts are and
OL,9,Fhow to mitigate the risks."
OL,11,FPoliticians also decided to store
OL,12,Fwater at Les Vardes Quarry which means
OL,13,Fprevious suggestions that it could be
OL,14,Fused as a water park or an outdoor
OL,15,Ftheatre will now not happen.
OL,17,FWith quarrying moving to the Chouet
OL,18,FHeadland soon, the committee for
OL,19,FEnvironment & Infrastructure decided
OL,20,Fit was a good place to store water to
OL,21,Fsafeguard future supply.
