OL,6,FOn Wednesday (30 April), Deputy Mark
OL,7,FHelyar argued in the States that the
OL,8,Ftwo proposals, on Les Vardes and Black
OL,9,FRock, be brought to the assembly
OL,10,Fseparately rather than in the same
OL,11,Fproposition.
OL,13,FHe said "the two issues are not linked
OL,14,For in any way co-dependent" arguing
OL,15,Fthat Guernsey "cannot afford these
OL,16,Fplans (at Les Vardes), even if they
OL,17,Fwere credible and imminently pressing,
OL,18,Fwhich they are not."
